{
  "id": "5ad0476781d0150014009c35",
  "title": "塩澤先生の授業の体験記",
  "created": 1523599214,
  "updated": 1532093242,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ad0476781d0150014009c35",
      "text": "塩澤先生の授業の体験記",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599214,
      "updated": 1523601911
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad047c1aff09e000066aec6",
      "text": " 2018年4月から成蹊大学の塩澤先生[/shiology]の民法IIを聴講している",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599298,
      "updated": 1523601367
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad047c3aff09e000066aec9",
      "text": "  聴講生という仕組み自体の体験記はこちら: [聴講生・科目等履修生申し込み体験記]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599299,
      "updated": 1523599467
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad053bdaff09e000066af15",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523602365,
      "updated": 1523602365
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad0485faff09e000066aecb",
      "text": " 「自分が近い将来、フルの授業を持つ可能性がある」という気持ちで授業を受けるのは初めて",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599455,
      "updated": 1523599483
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad0487daff09e000066aecd",
      "text": "  非常勤講師で一枠だけ話すのは何度かやったけど、やっぱり1時間話すのと毎週1時間を12回とか話すのは別物",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599485,
      "updated": 1523599509
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04895aff09e000066aece",
      "text": "  正直シラバスとか何を考えて作ればいいかよくわからない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599509,
      "updated": 1523599526
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04906aff09e000066aed0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599623,
      "updated": 1523599623
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04906aff09e000066aed1",
      "text": "\t習ってる民法の話をここでまとめるつもりはない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599623,
      "updated": 1523599658
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04929aff09e000066aed2",
      "text": " \t改めて「なぜまとめる気がないのか」を考えてみると興味深い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599658,
      "updated": 1523601813
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04b10aff09e000066aeee",
      "text": "  \t考えてみた: [アウトプットを焦ると劣化コピーになる]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600145,
      "updated": 1524148420
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad05200aff09e000066af13",
      "text": "\t\tというわけで「民法II体験記」でも「聴講生体験記」でもないのでこんなタイトルになった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523601920,
      "updated": 1523602272
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad05200aff09e000066af14",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523601920,
      "updated": 1523602379
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04873aff09e000066aecc",
      "text": " 「教え合う学びが大事」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599475,
      "updated": 1523599679
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad0493faff09e000066aed4",
      "text": " \tこれは僕も首都大の授業で3年に渡り言い続けた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599679,
      "updated": 1523599691
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad0494aaff09e000066aed5",
      "text": "   [互いに知識を交換して学ぶ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599691,
      "updated": 1523599727
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad0494aaff09e000066aed6",
      "text": "  が、それを授業内で実現する方法は思いつかなかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599691,
      "updated": 1523599736
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04977aff09e000066aed7",
      "text": "  授業が終わってから各自がやるイメージだった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599736,
      "updated": 1523599741
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad0497caff09e000066aed8",
      "text": "  塩澤先生のバディを作るメソッドは有用",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599741,
      "updated": 1523599741
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad049c1aff09e000066aedb",
      "text": "  \t事前に大きな紙が配布してある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599809,
      "updated": 1523599817
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04903aff09e000066aecf",
      "text": "   「民法は何のためにあるか」みたいな「正解のない問」について5分くらいとって紙に書かせる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599620,
      "updated": 1523599823
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad049cfaff09e000066aedc",
      "text": "   \t5行以上書くように言う",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599823,
      "updated": 1523599828
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad049d5aff09e000066aede",
      "text": "    [書き出し法]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599830,
      "updated": 1523599832
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad049cfaff09e000066aedd",
      "text": "   次にバディ(相棒)を探させる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599823,
      "updated": 1523599873
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04a03aff09e000066aee0",
      "text": "   \tペアを組みましょう的な僕の苦手なやつ！",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599875,
      "updated": 1523599895
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04a16aff09e000066aee1",
      "text": "    バディのいない人は手を挙げると先生がマッチングしてくれる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599895,
      "updated": 1523599909
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04a1faff09e000066aee2",
      "text": "   バディに自分の考えた答えを説明する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599904,
      "updated": 1523599927
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04a36aff09e000066aee3",
      "text": "   説明を聞いた人は、説明を聞いたしるしに署名をする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599927,
      "updated": 1523599935
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04ca0aff09e000060180a",
      "text": "   [https://gyazo.com/25c557205fe341e95546d76e3f3d006d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600545,
      "updated": 1523600546
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04ca2aff09e000060180b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t署名は一応消しておいた",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600546,
      "updated": 1532093242
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04a4baff09e000066aee5",
      "text": "\t\t複数人に回答を発表させて多様性を可視化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599948,
      "updated": 1523600181
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04a4baff09e000066aee4",
      "text": "  \t[正解がない]を実感させる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599948,
      "updated": 1523600187
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04b37aff09e000066aeef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600184,
      "updated": 1523600199
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04992aff09e000066aed9",
      "text": " 「書いて考える」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523599762,
      "updated": 1523600019
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04a89aff09e000066aee8",
      "text": "  僕は講義資料にかなり情報を入れてしまうタイプ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600010,
      "updated": 1523600024
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad0a0c4aff09e000060180f",
      "text": "   [講演スライドは著作]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523622084,
      "updated": 1523622133
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04a97aff09e000066aee9",
      "text": "   それによって聴衆は常に画面を見ていなければならなくなるから「書いて考える」ことができない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600024,
      "updated": 1523600024
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad0a100aff09e0000601810",
      "text": "   先生のスタイルの方がいいのかなぁ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523622144,
      "updated": 1523622173
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad0a11eaff09e0000601811",
      "text": "    [情報量多い資料を避けるべきか？]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523622174,
      "updated": 1523622195
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04a84aff09e000066aee7",
      "text": "\t\t逆に塩澤先生は、話と関係ないブログのトップページを開いたまま「法的三段論法、知ってる人？知らないの？すごく大事なことだよ？」と危機感を煽った上で、何も画面使わずに口頭だけで説明する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600004,
      "updated": 1523600061
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04ac3aff09e000066aeec",
      "text": "  画面に何も情報がないのだから耳でしっかり聞いて書き取るしかなくて、聴衆がみんな書くモードになっててうまい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600068,
      "updated": 1523600075
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04aadaff09e000066aeea",
      "text": "\t\tそしてそれが終わってから図解で説明して、心的イメージの補完をしててうまい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600046,
      "updated": 1523600091
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04adbaff09e000066aeed",
      "text": "\t\t「前の方の人はもう10行も書いてるぞ」という煽り",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600091,
      "updated": 1523600215
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04b58aff09e000066aef3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600216,
      "updated": 1523600216
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04b56aff09e000066aef2",
      "text": "\tまず授業前にQRコードが表示されている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600215,
      "updated": 1523600232
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04b68aff09e000066aef4",
      "text": " \tそのQRコードを開くと、Scrapbox",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600232,
      "updated": 1523600241
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04b74aff09e000066aef5",
      "text": "  それ自体にQRコードが貼られている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600245,
      "updated": 1523600279
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04b97aff09e000066aef6",
      "text": "  \tスクリーンに出ている間にQRの撮影ができなかった人は周囲の人に取らせてもらえばよい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600279,
      "updated": 1523600279
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04b4eaff09e000066aef1",
      "text": "\t\t\tうまい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600207,
      "updated": 1523600284
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04baeaff09e000066aefa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600302,
      "updated": 1523600302
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04b9caff09e000066aef8",
      "text": "\tScrapboxのプレゼンモードを使わない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600284,
      "updated": 1523600311
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04bb8aff09e000066aefb",
      "text": " \tジェスチャーでのスクロール、ズームでやる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600313,
      "updated": 1523600349
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04d46aff09e000066af05",
      "text": "\t\t先で話すことの質問をされたらシュッとスクロールして見せて「この後話す予定」をチラ見せ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600710,
      "updated": 1523600730
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04cefaff09e000066aefe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600623,
      "updated": 1523600623
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04bdcaff09e000066aefc",
      "text": "\t後ろ3列に座ってはいけないルール",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600349,
      "updated": 1523600639
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04cfeaff09e000066aeff",
      "text": " 発言回数が平常点になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600639,
      "updated": 1523600655
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04d0baff09e000066af00",
      "text": " \t当てられて発言したものを自分でカウントする",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600652,
      "updated": 1523600670
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04d1eaff09e000066af01",
      "text": "  発言の内容は問わない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600670,
      "updated": 1523600685
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04d2daff09e000066af02",
      "text": "  同時に手が上がったら前の席が優先のルール",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600685,
      "updated": 1523600699
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04d3baff09e000066af03",
      "text": "  \tすごいインセンティブづくり",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600699,
      "updated": 1523600705
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04d78aff09e000066af07",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600761,
      "updated": 1523600761
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04d5faff09e000066af06",
      "text": "\t過去問はブログに全部ある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600735,
      "updated": 1523600768
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04d80aff09e000066af08",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600768,
      "updated": 1523600769
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04d43aff09e000066af04",
      "text": "\t条文を全員で音読",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600708,
      "updated": 1523600735
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04fb8aff09e000066af10",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523601337,
      "updated": 1523601337
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04db0aff09e000066af09",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600816,
      "updated": 1523600816
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04fb7aff09e000066af0f",
      "text": "\tiPadからAirPlayで表示しているっぽい",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523601335,
      "updated": 1523601335
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04dc1aff09e000066af0b",
      "text": "\t大きくてしっかりしたピンマイクを付けている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600834,
      "updated": 1523600914
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04e11aff09e000066af0c",
      "text": " \tマイクを手に持ったらiPad+Pencilでのプレゼンはできないからねぇ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600914,
      "updated": 1523600938
    },
    {
      "id": "5ad04e29aff09e000066af0d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1523600938,
      "updated": 1523601339
    }
  ]
}